highlights.text: “BON” by Number_i has been on Viral Songs Japan the longest, at 442 days straight.
“Love Story” by c4nmooztury is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Japan, up 25 spots at #28.
TENBLANK has the most spots on Viral Songs Japan. “旋律と結晶” is the highest at #7.
